{
  "info": {
    "name": "LMS Backend API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Learning Management System (LMS) Backend. This collection includes all endpoints for authentication, user management, course management, enrollments, and more.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. **Set Environment Variables**: Configure the base URL and authentication token\n2. **Authentication**: Start with the Authentication folder to register/login and get your JWT token\n3. **Set Token**: After login, copy the token and set it in the Authorization header for protected routes\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- `base_url`: Your API base URL (e.g., http://localhost:5000)\n- `auth_token`: JWT token received after login\n\n## Authentication Flow\n\n1. Register a new user or login with existing credentials\n2. Copy the JWT token from the response\n3. Use the token in Authorization header as `Bearer {{auth_token}}`\n\n## Sample Credentials (after seeding)\n\n- **Admin**: admin@lms.com / Admin123!\n- **Instructor**: instructor@lms.com / Instructor123!\n- **Student**: student@lms.com / Student123!",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12345678",
    "_collection_link": "https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/12345678/lms-backend-api/1.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "User authentication endpoints including registration, login, profile management, and password operations.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"role\": \"student\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user account. Available roles: 'student', 'instructor'. Admin accounts must be created separately.\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- firstName: 2-50 characters\n- lastName: 2-50 characters\n- email: Valid email address\n- password: Minimum 6 characters with uppercase, lowercase, and number\n- role: 'student' or 'instructor'\n\n**Response:**\n- Returns JWT token and user profile\n- Token expires in 7 days (configurable)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Successful Registration",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"role\": \"student\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"User registered successfully\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"_id\": \"507f1f77bcf86cd799439011\",\n    \"firstName\": \"John\",\n    \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n    \"email\": \"john.doe@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"student\",\n    \"isActive\": true,\n    \"isEmailVerified\": false,\n    \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
