            "description": "Get all published courses with filtering, searching, and pagination.\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- page: Page number (default: 1)\n- limit: Items per page (default: 10, max: 50)\n- category: Filter by category\n- level: beginner, intermediate, advanced\n- price: free, paid\n- search: Search in title and description\n- sort: newest, oldest, popular, rating, price_low, price_high\n\n**Response:**\n- Array of courses with pagination info\n- Includes instructor information\n- Only published courses are returned"
