            },
            "description": "Update course information (Course instructor or Admin only).\n\n**Parameters:**\n- id: Course ID\n\n**Authorization:**\n- Only course instructor or admin can update\n- Some fields cannot be updated once published\n\n**Updatable Fields:**\n- title, description, shortDescription\n- price, duration, tags\n- prerequisites, learningObjectives\n- targetAudience, requirements"
          },
          "response": []
        },
