            "description": "Publish or unpublish a course.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- id: Course ID\n\n**Body:**\n- isPublished: true to publish, false to unpublish\n\n**Effects:**\n- Published courses are visible to students\n- Unpublished courses are only visible to instructors and admins\n- Publishing sets the publishedAt timestamp"
